# VSCode Browser Compatibility Checker (ms-edgedevtools.vscode-browser-compatibility).
#
# Coverage rationale:
#   Chrome / Edge / Opera / Samsung Internet — Chromium engine (last 2 major)
#   Firefox / FirefoxAndroid              — Gecko engine (last 2 major)
#   Safari / iOS                          — WebKit engine (last 2 major + iOS 16.4+)
#   UCAndroid / QQAndroid                 — Chromium-based; kept for API baseline check
#   not dead                              — removes browsers with <0.5% global share

